OL,3,CSome air fares more than quadruple as
OL,4,Cconflict drives price surge
OL,6,FSome air fares have more than
OL,7,Fquadrupled in recent days, amid a
OL,8,Fscramble to re-book cancelled flights,
OL,9,FITV News understands.
OL,11,FConflict in the Middle East has left
OL,12,Fthousands of airline passengers
OL,13,Fdiverted, with many left stranded.
OL,15,FAnd the chaos caused by the closure of
OL,16,Fairspace has led to skyrocketing
OL,17,Fprices for those who are trying to re-
OL,18,Fbook. Experts say a growing number of
OL,19,Ftravellers face a price shock.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
