OL,3,CSome air fares more than quadruple as
OL,4,Cconflict drives price surge
OL,6,FAirfares on many affected routes are
OL,7,Frising:
OL,9,FOne customer told ITV News that she
OL,10,Fsaw no alternative other than to pay
OL,11,Fmore than the over #2,000 to get home
OL,12,Ffrom Oman in the Middle East.
OL,14,F"I paid #2,128 to get back, but a one-
OL,15,Fway flight economy should have only
OL,16,Fcost me maximum #400," Seema Thakker
OL,17,Ftold ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
