CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772744764
OL,3,CSome air fares more than quadruple as
OL,4,Cconflict drives price surge
OL,6,F"It's unfair because they're putting
OL,7,Fpeople in debt. I met people that
OL,8,Fliterally had to get credit cards out
OL,9,Fto pay for their flights just to get
OL,10,Fhome for their safety."
OL,12,FWith homecomings at such huge cost,
OL,13,Findustry insiders blame market forces.
OL,14,FAviation expert Anita Mendiratta told
OL,15,FITV News that prices had risen due to
OL,16,Fthe reduced flight capacity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772744764
OL,3,CSome air fares more than quadruple as
OL,4,Cconflict drives price surge
OL,6,F"Capacity has gone down, because many
OL,7,Fof the traditional carriers in the
OL,8,FMiddle East, incredibly strong,
OL,9,Fexceptional carriers like Qatar
OL,10,FAirways, Emirates and Etihad, they are
OL,11,Fsimply not able to fly at the capacity
OL,12,Fthey're used to," she said.
OL,14,FAnd the financial effect on travellers
OL,15,Fis now spreading farther beyond the
OL,16,FMiddle Eastern hub airports, because
OL,17,Falternative flights and holidays are
OL,18,Fbeing snapped up.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
