OL,3,CSome air fares more than quadruple as
OL,4,Cconflict drives price surge
OL,6,FAviation officials say airfares
OL,7,Fbetween Thailand and Europe have risen
OL,8,Fby up to 100%. Travel Consultant Paul
OL,9,FCharles told ITV News that this was
OL,10,Fdue to a shift in demand.
OL,12,F"Because demand is shifting from the
OL,13,FMiddle East to other destinations
OL,14,Faround the world, it's forcing
OL,15,Fpressure on prices. Prices are going
OL,16,Fup, not only of airline seats but of
OL,17,Fhotels as well," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
